        <h1 id="care-provision">Care provision</h1>
        <p>We promote the independence of clients by supporting them at home. Care calls range from 15 minute pop in visits to one hour and above. Clients structure these calls to suit their needs.</p>
        <p>The services we provide range from:</p>
        <ul class="dots">
          <li>Assistance in the morning, including helping clients get out of bed, wash, bath, get dressed and have breakfast</li>
          <li>Shopping for or with a client</li>
          <li>Preparation of food</li>
          <li>Medication prompting</li>
          <li>Domestic tasks such as laundry, ironing and cleaning</li>
          <li>Bathing</li>
          <li>Assistance with evening care routine</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To discuss your requirements, please <a href="contact.html">contact us</a> or call us on <a href="tel:01344876099" class="tel">01344 876099</a>. If you wish to go ahead, we will then arrange an appointment for you, normally with our Care Manager Olivia Macleay, to construct a suitable Care Plan.</p>
